%F A046184 Nearest integer to (1/6) * (2+sqrt(3))^(2n-1). - _Ralf Stephan_, Feb 24 2004
%F A046184 a(n) = A045899(n-1) + 1 = A051047(n+1) + 1 = A003697(2n-2). - _N. J. A. Sloane_, Jun 12 2004
